# 🦠 COVID-19 Dashboard (Power BI)

## 📌 Overview
This project presents an interactive COVID-19 dashboard developed using Microsoft Power BI. The dashboard provides insights into confirmed cases, recoveries, deaths, and vaccination trends across different regions.

## 🎯 Objectives
- Analyze the global and regional spread of COVID-19.
- Visualize trends in confirmed, recovered, and death cases.
- Provide interactive insights using filters and slicers.
- Support data-driven decision-making.

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Power BI
- Microsoft Excel / CSV
- Data Visualization
- Data Cleaning and Transformation (Power Query)

## 📊 Dashboard Features
- Total confirmed, recovered, and death cases.
- Country-wise and region-wise analysis.
- Time-series trends of COVID-19 cases.
- Interactive filters and slicers.
- Vaccination progress (if included).


